<section class="system_requirements_section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-7 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                <h2>Sensor Hardware</h2>
                <div class="box_contain_part">
                    <p>This device features a FAP10 capacitive sensor with a 500 dpi pixel resolution and a platen size of 12.8mm x 18mm. It captures images at 256 x 360 pixels and has a maximum acquisition time of less than 2 seconds. The device has a low FRR & FAR of less than 0.1% & 0.001%, and supports latent finger detection. It has an MTBF of 50000 hours and a wear & tear cycle of 1 million. The module has dimensions of 35mm X 23mm X 5mm, and the device itself measures 58.1mm x 33.3mm x 12mm and weighs approximately 0.040 kg. The sensor also undergoes rigorous testing, including a SALT spray test, cross cut test, and surface hardness test.</p>
