                <h2>Certification</h2>
                <div class="box_contain_part">
                    <p>This device uses ISO 19794-2:2005 & 2011 and ANSI 378 for biometric data interchange. It is compliant with CE & FCC Part 15B class A for EMI/EMC and has ESD protection of +/- 8kV (contact discharge) and +/- 15kV (air discharge). The device is RoHS compliant and meets EN/IEC 62368-1 and IS 13252 safety standards. It has FBI PIV certification for image quality and Mobile-ID FAP10. The device has an IP54 rating at the device level and IP67 rating in the platen area, and its device driver is WHQL certified.</p>
